Godwin Isenyo, Kaduna Gunmen on Sunday reportedly kidnapped the Chairman of the Kaura Local Government Area of Kaduna State, Mr Katuka Humble. It was gathered that the incident took place at Kiduni village in the Chikun Local Government Area of the state. A source said Humble was being conveyed to his farm on a motorcycle when the hoodlums opened fire, killing the rider on the spot. The gunmen were said to have subsequently gone away with the chairman. “The farm is located somewhere around Kiduni in Chikun LGA,” the source said. As of the time of filing this report, the Public Relations Officer of the state police command, ASP Mohammed Jalige, could not be reached and there was no reply to a text message sent to his telephone. Copyright PUNCH.
